<br>
When you zone the server strips all of your equipment off of you. So if you zone with less hit points then the hit points on your equipment you are at neg hit points. When you zone back in the server put's your equipment back on you. Now you are both dead and alive, the server thinks something is wrong and <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> strips all your buffs</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> and sends you to the safe spot in the zone.  <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=144471>Malthorn</a>
